Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.35,0:00:06.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.76,0:00:08.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:16.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:26.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:29.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:35.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.52,0:00:41.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:48.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:53.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.25,0:00:55.31,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.58,0:01:13.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.03,0:01:16.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.23,0:01:21.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:27.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, let's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.99,0:01:35.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.04,0:01:39.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.17,0:01:41.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.79,0:01:46.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.15,0:01:48.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.85,0:01:50.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:52.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.23,0:01:53.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.89,0:01:55.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:57.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:01:58.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:00.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.59,0:02:01.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:06.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:08.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.58,0:02:14.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:19.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:21.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:25.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:32.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.85,0:02:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.73,0:02:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.21,0:02:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.36,0:02:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:03:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.31,0:03:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hit him with the light!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.10,0:03:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerk, I'll get you for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.46,0:03:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?! My shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.55,0:03:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've obtained 300 million\NBerries' worth of might!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can complete the greatest\NSpecial Zombie in history!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.72,0:04:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Warrior Known as the 'Devil'!!\NThe Moment of Oars' Revival!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.59,0:04:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Straw Hat Luffy belongs to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:05:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At last! I've finally obtained\Nthe ultimate subordinate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Luffy...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened? Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.63,0:05:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's his shadow! He cut off Luffy's shadow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.81,0:05:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His shadow...? Didn't that skeleton,\NBrook, mention something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He stole Luffy's shadow?\NIs he the one who took Brook's?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.44,0:05:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it... How did he do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kumacy! You were mumbling\Nsomething again, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you to zip it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.29,0:05:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it through your head!\NI'm tired of repeating myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not cute when you talk, so don't talk!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:06:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too harsh on Kumacy.\NYou're beary harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you goofing off, punk?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.82,0:06:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shut up" means "be quiet"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This shadow will bring me one step closer
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to becoming the King of the Pirates, Hogback!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a decade since we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I put all of my prowess into creating\NNo. 900 for a day such as this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.89,0:06:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that shadow in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain it'll become the\Nmost powerful zombie in history!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be a great asset!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.31,0:06:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day I become the world's\N"King of the Grave" is close at hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.96,0:06:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can practically see the day I turn\Nthe cute critters of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.42,0:07:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,into zombies and make them\Nserve me in my dream kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.35,0:07:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! You can command absolute loyalty\Nfrom the shadow of the nastiest bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.71,0:07:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world will transform into a\Nland filled with obedient zombies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd had a subordinate as powerful as this,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that idiot Kaido never would have\Ndefeated me in the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.13,0:07:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wake him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.68,0:07:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyoro! Nin! Bao!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open the door to the special freezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.78,0:07:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right away, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.48,0:07:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, No. 900.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.03,0:07:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm bringing the ultimate shadow down to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.84,0:07:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so be quick about making\Nme King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.23,0:07:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spider Mouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toss Straw Hat Luffy's body onto the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:08:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget to remove the spider silk.\NWe can't have him dying on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.99,0:08:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Roger!\N--One moment! I need to make a report!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.07,0:08:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Tararan, the spider monkey,\Nwas just defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.06,0:08:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was defeated?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as though the foe removed his shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's exactly what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.92,0:08:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He lost his shadow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.01,0:08:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.68,0:08:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absalom, there is only one\Nman who could do that...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.22,0:08:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Humming Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like Hildon's report\Nwas accurate after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the Humming Swordsman\Nis removing shadows wherever he goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've already suffered heavy losses\Nbefore anyone realized he was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.89,0:08:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, we're going to relive\Nthe nightmare of five years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! We have to go back to the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Sunny?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:09:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. The worst they'll do\Nto your captured crewmates
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.76,0:09:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is steal their shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.65,0:09:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not as though that's fatal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at me! I'm a prime example.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I actually did die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's a different story!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.38,0:09:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When ya get down to it, it's not\Nlike losing your shadow'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely! But the thing is,\Neveryone falls unconscious
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.64,0:09:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when their shadow is snatched away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.57,0:09:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They won't awaken for two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.56,0:09:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stronger the person,\Nthe sooner he is put on a ship
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and kicked out of Thriller Bark.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.27,0:09:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think they'd do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To prevent the victims from returning\Nto the island to recover their shadows?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.49,0:09:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't they kill us\Nwhen we're out cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.66,0:09:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is important, so pay attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.05,0:10:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, even if you separate\Na person from his shadow,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they are still of one mind and body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the human dies, the shadow will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.76,0:10:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means the zombie will die then as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.03,0:10:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wouldn't serve the enemy's needs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hence they always keep the human body alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So even if your friends lose their shadows,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.65,0:10:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise they will get sent\Nback to your ship alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.96,0:10:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The worst case scenario would be for\Nthe two of you to fall victim as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would mean that all of you are doomed\Nto wander the ocean without your shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awaken your friends while\Nthere is still time to act!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only chance you get to look\Nfor a way to recover their shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you understand all of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Everything sounds logical enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.69,0:11:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, guys, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The zombies' weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.12,0:11:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw how effective it was in my\Nbattle against this spider monkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the zombie's "soul."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His soul?! But I can see it leaving his body!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.51,0:11:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's high time you returned...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.26,0:11:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to your rightful master!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.62,0:11:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is their weakness? What exactly is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.41,0:12:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Salt?! If we gotta purify\Nthe things to take 'em out,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are they some kinda curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose they are in a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.02,0:12:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The zombies were originally\Nanimated thanks to a Devil Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.32,0:12:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Salt holds the power of the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.80,0:12:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So just as a power holder\Ngrows limp in the ocean,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the salt breaks the fusion\Nbetween a fake soul and a body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.52,0:12:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makes sense! So that monkey spewed out\Nthe shadow that was inside of him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That never would have occurred to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To reiterate, please stuff salt into\Na zombie's mouth to defeat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the trick! Even for this\Nbag of bones, that's a snap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.51,0:12:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Snap! Snap! Snap!\N--But Brook...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so knowledgeable\Nabout the zombies and this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.61,0:12:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That has to do with when I lost\Nmy shadow five years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.05,0:12:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, they sent me back out to drift at sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:13:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, I was able to\Nturn back by the time I awoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And thus I returned to the island and fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.64,0:13:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I faced the zombie who holds my shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, I lost miserably.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fled for fear of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.22,0:13:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what, I did not want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the sole survivor from my ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday I must pull out of the Devil's Sea
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and carry out the promise I made to my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.16,0:13:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I ran for my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.84,0:14:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But ultimately, extending my\Nlife did not resolve anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I am done running!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.44,0:14:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I defeat that man and recover my--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.62,0:14:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you'll have to pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.07,0:14:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a hurry. Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.43,0:14:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of everything you've told us,\Nanswer this one question before you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Humming...!\NGrah, the Humming Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.32,0:15:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! He's the only person to have\Nfigured out my zombies' weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Huh? How did he figure\Nit out in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And how did he come back--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Cindry-chan! Why do you\Nkeep standing in front of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humming Swordsman...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard about him, but what is he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.86,0:15:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perona! Don't you know what he looks like?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.16,0:15:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would explain how he\Nslipped through your recon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it would seem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, the seed of trouble\Nhas returned to our island.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of my concern, simpleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.23,0:16:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can deal with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.21,0:16:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.21,0:16:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.96,0:16:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let's go to the freezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.22,0:16:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir...! The present condition is such...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.62,0:16:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! You should have mentioned that first!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, he should\Nbuy us plenty of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.83,0:16:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.13,0:16:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come report to me if there\Nare any other problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now go toss Straw Hat out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, go! Heave, ho! Heave, ho! Heave, ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.24,0:16:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heave, ho! Heave, ho! Heave, ho!\NHeave, ho! Heave, ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.16,0:16:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy!\N--Stupid! Don't pop out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't die just because they took his shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.68,0:16:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.39,0:16:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.23,0:16:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumacy, hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't leave now! Let's bide our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to do something\Nwith Luffy's shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.61,0:17:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta find out what!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can worry about recovering it later!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That duo is long gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected them to defeat Tararan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.33,0:17:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here's the spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.68,0:17:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez! Did you get lost, Jigoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.59,0:17:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Off my back! Now where are my foes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me face them now! Give me enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, punk? I'm not crying, you dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.14,0:17:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:18:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What compelled you... to ask him that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I can ask whatever I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.49,0:18:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh darn it! I freaking love that skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never find a better guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.68,0:18:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.77,0:18:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They really are scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.54,0:19:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The Humming Swordsman... is terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.38,0:19:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.91,0:19:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never, ever give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.59,0:20:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will recover my shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.95,0:20:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.10,0:20:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I saw his corpse in the Land of Ice,\Nmy body wouldn't stop trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.99,0:20:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's breathtaking when you\Nthink that this terrifying beast
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.42,0:20:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,used to terrorize the seas 500 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.70,0:20:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Cold!\N--When he conquered a nation, he'd carry\Nthe entire island back to his domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.09,0:21:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's said he created a kingdom of thugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.50,0:21:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so close to the famous giant\Nknown as the legendary "Continent Puller."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.61,0:21:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.77,0:21:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the heck are they going?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.51,0:21:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me, but I think they said\Nsomething about a special freezer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That explains it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.91,0:21:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Land of Ice? A corpse?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.85,0:21:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never dreamed I'd get to see\Nthat legend with my own two eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a zombie creator's--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Cindry-chan! Why are\Nyou walking in front of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.15,0:21:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet another legend shall come back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.96,0:21:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, No. 900.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.56,0:22:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it's time for him to awaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.55,0:22:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the only berserker to have\Ngone down in history as a "Devil."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.48,0:22:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oars!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.43,0:23:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? They put\NLuffy's shadow in that giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.78,0:23:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've finally uncovered the\Nsecret behind the zombies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.47,0:23:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! Let go! What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.78,0:23:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.97,0:23:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that invisible man again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.12,0:23:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami, you're... vanishing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.23,0:23:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.98,0:23:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.98,0:23:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Awakening After 500 Years!!\NOars Opens His Eyes!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.27,0:23:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
